---
surface: verify_time_budget
bead: bd-3usjw.39
schema: ee.closure_surface_golden.v1
purpose: scripts/verify.sh reports and enforces per-stage elapsed-time budgets.
budget_manifest: scripts/verify-budget.toml
primary_tests:
  - tests/verification_drift_guard.rs
checks:
  - Every verify.sh run_stage entry has a matching budget manifest stage.
  - Every stage declares expected_seconds_p50 and regression_factor = 1.5.
  - Non-benchmark p50 budgets sum to the 10-minute readiness target.
  - Budget status reports ok, advisory, or fail for each stage.
verified_by:
  - cargo test --test verification_drift_guard verify_budget
  - cargo test --test verification_drift_guard verify_sh_reports_and_enforces_stage_budgets

